dct_title_s: Misamis, Philippine Islands, Misamis Occidental Province. A.M.S. S901
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: Misamis. In upper left margin: Philippine Islands city plans. Depth shown in soundings by fathoms at mean lower low water. Copied from U.S.C.&G.S. Chart 4640. From surveys in 1906 with additions from Spanish survey in 1896,.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1944.
